Mother-in-law suite with own full bathroom with split plan and master suite in another side with 2 walk-in closets, open concept living room, formal dining, Wood laminate flooring, breakfast bar and eat-in kitchen, granite kitchen counter tops in kitchen and all bathroom matching counter tops.
